<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This document supplements the quarterly legal aid statistics bulletin by providing a comprehensive guide to the statistics and how to use them.</p>

<p>It provides a brief background overview of the legal aid system including recent reforms, and it also covers:</p>

<ul>
  <li>explanations of terminology</li>
  <li>data sources and quality</li>
  <li>revisions policy</li>
  <li>users and uses of the statistics</li>
  <li>other explanatory notes</li>
</ul>

<p>For users of the detailed data published in csv format each quarter, a separate guide to the more detailed data is published alongside each quarterly legal aid statistics bulletin.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

